===Spending=== 
Users can spend their VRChat Credits on the {{VRC link|https://vrchat.com/home/marketplace/welcome |website}}, or in the client, through either, the [[Special:MyLanguage/Shop|Shop]], or [[Special:MyLanguage/Avatars|avatar]], [[Special:MyLanguage/Groups|group]], or [[Special:MyLanguage/Worlds|world]] stores. Users can buy a listing or a subscription with their VRChat Credits, each listing and subscription has products attached to them, these are ''in layman's terms'' the benefits you receive from the listing or subscription. 

The '''Spotlight''' section of the Marketplace tab offers suggestions of worlds and groups that are currently enrolled in the Creator Economy Program.

For more creator-related information, see the Creator Economy documentation<ref>{{VRC link|https://creators.vrchat.com/economy/|Creator Economy Documentation}} from 24 May, 2024</ref>''.''

====Stores====
Stores are where users can buy content with VRChat Credits. There are 3 types of stores:
