==== Listings====
Listings are what users can buy from stores. While listings can be anything the creator decides, users can expect to see common types of listing such as: Unlocking new areas of a world, customization options, and more.

There are 3 types of listings creators can offer, each type has a different duration type.
{| class="wikitable"
! Listing 
!Duration
! Description 
|-
|Instant
|None
|Users can purchase this type as many times as they want. Benefits are instantly awarded. This type is only purchasable if you are in the world.
|-
| Temporary
|5 minutes - 3 months
|Users can purchase this type as many times as they want '''but''' can't repurchase until its duration expires. Benefits earned are only available until its duration expires.
|-
|Permanent
|Unlimited
|Users can only purchase this type once. Benefits are permanently available to the buyer.
|}

=====Subscriptions=====
Subscriptions are the type of listing that users can buy from group stores. While listings can be anything the world creator decides, users can expect to see common types of listing such as: VIP access.

Users have 4 default duration options, they can choose from when buying a subscription.  

*1 month
* 3 months
*6 months
*12 months

There is also a custom duration option users can choose, which ranges from 1 month to 99 months. Subscriptions do not automatically renew.

When a user buys a subscription, they will be automatically added to the group they bought the subscription from. Buyers will also a group role, which creators can offer group specific benefits. 

